{
  "stem": "24268.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe later, when I-- anyway, she asked me to make a biography.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She knew I was into drawing with a pencil.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And actually, we had none.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She brought me some little card, about that size.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said she was going to-- she asked me to make the biography, the whole how we arrived, how it happened, how we-- the [NON-ENGLISH], how they counted.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They counted four in a row.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the whole camp was on one-- twice a day they used to count us, so somebody didn't escape or whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she told me she-- after how it was the SS took us over, the whole picture.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had to describe the [NON-ENGLISH], and the SS, how they took us over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then she told me that she was going to put this in a letter and give us a gift to the [NON-ENGLISH] this, to the Branca Weinstock.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A gift to the [NON-ENGLISH], to the head of the Jew-- of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was Branca Weinstein-- Weinstock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I-- she lives now in Israel, in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I called her when I was there, but she wasn't home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her daughter answered the phone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was in London.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't say why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wanted my kids-- they said-- now I am impossible for me to be able to concentrate, and to bring all this back life, the way it was, to reproduce the same thing.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was difficult for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, maybe if she would be nice enough, she'd still had it, to make a copy for the children to show, for my grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she never respond.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wrote a letter to her and she never respond to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why did she asked you to write all this down?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
